voices.description: A middle-aged, deep male voice, robust and powerful like rolling thunder. The tone is authoritative, weathered, and gravelly, carrying the weight of countless battles. It has a resonant, booming quality in its main cadence, yet can drop into low, wise whispers like a wind crossing a wasteland. The delivery is measured, loyal, and profoundly commanding, with a sharp, metallic edge reminiscent of iron armor. Perfect for prophecies and revealing hid

voices.name: Dantalion
voices.description: A middle-aged, non-binary, androgynous voice with an intelligent, analytical quality. The tone is smooth, controlled, and coolly resonant, with a slight air of detachment. The cadence is deliberate, often dropping into persuasive, confidential whispers that feel like thoughts carried on a wind. It has a slender, sharp, and clear timbre, like silver, with a neutral, accentless precision perfect for revealing secrets and complex ideas.

voices.name: Crocell
voices.description: An adult, non-binary, androgynous voice, thin and expressive. The tone is communicative and calming, with an air of mystique. It has the fluid, lilting cadence of flowing water—soft and clear, sometimes dropping to a gentle, teaching whisper. There's a slight gravelly undertone, like water over stones, and a neutral, clear accent perfect for narration and teaching.

voices.name: Bune
voices.description: "A wise and benevolent elderly female voice, old but robust. Speak with an enchanting, lyrical cadence, at a measured, deliberate pace. The tone should be deep and resonant, with a warm, gravelly texture that conveys ancient wisdom and authority. Use a neutral, slightly Eastern-accented English. Perfect audio quality for a commanding, mystical character
